(defrule start (and (not (exists (wynik ? $?))) (not (exists (pytanie ? $?))) (not (exists (odpowiedz ?)))) => (assert (pytanie "Classic or modern?" "I need an escape from Tinder" "I'm a modern girl.")))
(defrule need-an-escape ?id <- (odpowiedz "I need an escape from Tinder") ?pid <- (pytanie $?) => (retract ?id) (retract ?pid) (assert (pytanie "Black and white?" "Definitely, love oldies!" "Lets go more modern.")))
(defrule answer-ex1 ?id <- (odpowiedz "Definitely, love oldies!") ?pid <- (pytanie $?) => (retract ?id) (retract ?pid) (assert (wynik "Wynik 1")))
(defrule answer-ex2 ?id <- (odpowiedz "Lets go more modern.") ?pid <- (pytanie $?) => (retract ?id) (retract ?pid) (assert (wynik "Wynik 2")))
(defrule answer-ex3 ?id <- (odpowiedz "I'm a modern girl.") ?pid <- (pytanie $?) => (retract ?id) (retract ?pid) (assert (wynik "Wynik 3")))